    <item>
      <title>中国加大刺激力度遏制市场暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-24/china-pumps-up-stimulus-to-stem-market-rout-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，将在两周内降低银行存款准备金率，并暗示将采取更多支持措施，因为北京方面希望提振经济并阻止 6 万亿美元的股市暴跌。彭博社贾斯蒂娜·李报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-24/china-pumps-up-stimulus-to-stem-market-rout-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 13:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富达和贝莱德在比特币 ETF 流量竞赛中占据主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/fidelity-and-blackrock-are-dominating-the-bitcoin-etf-flow-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国监管机构为十只现货比特币交易所交易基金打响发令枪后不到两周，它越来越看起来像是一场新资产的两匹马竞赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/fidelity-and-blackrock-are-dominating-the-bitcoin-etf-flow-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 13:54:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔塔钢铁因印度经济增长和成本下降而扭亏为盈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/tata-steel-swings-to-profit-as-india-growth-offsets-weak-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塔塔钢铁有限公司恢复盈利，其印度业务的强劲表现和较低的成本抵消了欧洲业务的疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/tata-steel-swings-to-profit-as-india-growth-offsets-weak-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 13:25:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国通过放宽贷款使用加大对开发商融资的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/china-beefs-up-support-for-developer-funding-by-easing-loan-uses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国监管机构通过扩大获得部分商业贷款的渠道，为陷入困境的开发商提供更多财政支持，这是在股市暴跌之际遏制房地产放缓和重振市场信心的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/china-beefs-up-support-for-developer-funding-by-easing-loan-uses</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 13:12:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管整体数据意外上升，墨西哥一月初核心通胀仍放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/mexico-headline-inflation-unexpectedly-sped-up-in-early-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥的总体通胀在今年前两周出人意料地加速，而受到密切关注的核心指标则放缓，因为央行行长表示他们将讨论最终开始降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/mexico-headline-inflation-unexpectedly-sped-up-in-early-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:11:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度公布公司直接在 GIFT City 上市的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/india-notifies-rules-for-direct-listing-of-firms-in-gift-city</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度公布了规定，允许其公司在古吉拉特邦的一个新金融中心的国际交易所上市，该国允许更容易的外国交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/india-notifies-rules-for-direct-listing-of-firms-in-gift-city</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 11:58:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国通过允许银行保留较小的准备金来刺激经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/pboc-will-cut-rrr-for-banks-in-early-february-governor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示将在两周内降低银行存款准备金率，并暗示将采取更多支持措施，这一异常提前的披露表明习近平主席政府提振经济和阻止 6 万亿美元股市暴跌的紧迫性越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/pboc-will-cut-rrr-for-banks-in-early-february-governor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 07:43:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
